data.text: Cerberus is a three-headed demon monster in Greek mythology. Cerberus guards the underworld for Hades to keep the dead in and keep the living out. Cerberus is primarily known for his capture by Hercules, the last of Hercules' twelve labors. Each head on our planter is a pot that you can add a plant to and each has its own drainage hole. This small planter is ideal for growing succulents, air plants, mini cacti, and herbs. Great for office or home. Decorate a mantel, shelf, window ledge or desktop.
